      "content": "Candidate 1 demonstrates superior communication by using clear, professional language and focusing on effective techniques like empathy and active listening. Their answers are articulate and directly suitable for a professional office environment where clarity and competence are expected. In contrast, Candidate 2's heavy use of slang, filler words, and run-on sentences makes their ideas difficult to understand and appears unprofessional for this role. While their underlying approach is similar, Candidate 1 is significantly better suited for a standard customer service position.",
